## Your Task

Based on the above information, decide on the next wave of {{ waves_parallel }} hyperparameter
configurations to evaluate. For each configuration:

1. Explain your reasoning (why you chose these values).
2. Provide the hyperparameters as a JSON object.
3. The orchestrator will launch the experiments and report back.

Think step by step. Consider what the history tells you about promising regions
of the search space and what areas remain unexplored.
